metadata.name: The Mercurial Place No. 2
metadata.description:
The Mercurial Place No. 1 is part of a series which, to me, represents the wide range and ever-changing emotions we experience in life. It is a canvas of swirling feelings which are constantly shifting and morphing, just like our mind and psyche in a given week, month, hour, or day.

With this purchase you will receive a full access membership to https://thestoicgentlemenclub.org/ To access the VIP Membership enter the password on the website and sign up. You also can receive one free 4x6 Print of the NFT. Just click the free print tab and enter the NFT Access Code provided (Access Code Only redeemable to first buyer)
